tasks.name: KIS Textual 1
descriptions: The camera pans around people running on a beach. Afterwards, the people are shown performing practice exercises on the beach, guided by an instructor.

The camera pans around people running on a beach. Afterwards, the people are shown performing practice exercises on the beach, guided by an instructor. They are practicing how to stand and how to get up on a surf board.

The camera pans around people running on a beach. Afterwards, the people are shown performing practice exercises on the beach, guided by an instructor. They are practicing how to stand and how to get up on a surf board. Everybody is wearing black wet-suits with long-sleeve shirts. The instructors shits are white, everyone else's are blue.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 2
descriptions: A video showing lions, a giraffe and elephants in the wild, in that order.
A video showing lions, a giraffe and elephants in the wild, in that order. The first two shots show one lion each, the second one has a mane.

A video showing lions, a giraffe and elephants in the wild, in that order. The first two shots show one lion each, the second one has a mane. The giraffe is first shown eating from a tree and then walking from left to right. The elephants are standing in water with a large one centered in the frame and two smaller ones to the side.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 3
descriptions: A small child climbs onto a glass table and then onto a bed standing next to the table and then jumps off the bed. In the next shot, the child is on the bed together with a man and a woman.

A small child climbs onto a glass table and then onto a bed standing next to the table and then jumps off the bed. In the next shot, the child is on the bed together with a man and a woman. When the child jumps from the bed, there is another person there taking pictures with a camera.

A small child climbs onto a glass table and then onto a bed standing next to the table and then jumps off the bed. In the next shot, the child is on the bed together with a man and a woman. When the child jumps from the bed, there is another person there taking pictures with a camera. The child wears bluejeans and a shirt with light-blue, dark-blue and yellow stripes.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 4
descriptions: A man wearing a rabbit mask shown from behind sitting on a pipe next to a body of water. The next shots show him walking down an alley between two rows of buildings and then pretending to eat some plant.

A man wearing a rabbit mask shown from behind sitting on a pipe next to a body of water. The next shots show him walking down an alley between two rows of buildings and then pretending to eat some plant. The plant is in a flowerpot on a chair in front of a building with a brown door and orange walls.

A man wearing a rabbit mask shown from behind sitting on a pipe next to a body of water. The next shots show him walking down an alley between two rows of buildings and then pretending to eat some plant. The plant is in a flowerpot on a chair in front of a building with a brown door and orange walls. There are English subtitles on the bottom of the screen for the voice over by another person which describes their thoughts and actions.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 5
descriptions: Close-up shots of blue armbands and colorful balloons, followed by a shot of a women holding a microphone standing next to two men. Multiple shots with these three adults talking alternating with shots of children sitting on the floor.

Close-up shots of blue armbands and colorful balloons, followed by a shot of a women holding a microphone standing next to two men. Multiple shots with these three adults talking alternating with shots of children sitting on the floor. One of the two man wears a light-blue tie and a gray jacket, the other wears a dark tie and a diagonally striped scarf.

Close-up shots of blue armbands and colorful balloons, followed by a shot of a women holding a microphone standing next to two men. Multiple shots with these three adults talking alternating with shots of children sitting on the floor. One of the two man wears a light-blue tie and a gray jacket, the other wears a dark tie and a diagonally striped scarf. The whole event is happening in a large hall with domed ceiling and a polished floor.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 6
descriptions: A man in a vest and with rolled-up sleeves is standing in front of a musical instrument gesturing. The next shot shows him from the back playing piano and the shot after that has him directly talking to the camera.

A man in a vest and with rolled-up sleeves is standing in front of a musical instrument gesturing. The next shot shows him from the back playing piano and the shot after that has him directly talking to the camera. The first shot is in a room with stacked stone walls and the instrument which is played similar to a piano has a light-blue color.

A man in a vest and with rolled-up sleeves is standing in front of a musical instrument gesturing. The next shot shows him from the back playing piano and the shot after that has him directly talking to the camera. The first shot is in a room with stacked stone walls and the instrument which is played similar to a piano has a light-blue color.  The man has brown hair and eyes and a beard and  in the last shot is wearing a blue shirt with a red and yellow line pattern.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 7
descriptions: The first two shots, taken by a flying camera, shows a large building on a beach. In the next shot, a man in a suit is talking into a microphone. The last shot shows a spinning ceiling fan.

The first two shots, taken by a flying camera, shows a large building on a beach. In the next shot, a man in a suit is talking into a microphone. The last shot shows a spinning ceiling fan. The man is a groom, standing across from his bride, reciting his wedging wows.

The first two shots, taken by a flying camera, shows a large building on a beach. In the next shot, a man in a suit is talking into a microphone. The last shot shows a spinning ceiling fan. The man is a groom, standing across from his bride, reciting his wedging wows. During the whole sequence, the man can be heard talking and a piano and a cello can be heard playing in the background.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 8
descriptions: Black and white shots of waves crashing against and around a small light house, afterwards fade to black. In the next shots, a person in a wet-suit is using a screwdriver and a knife to attach something to a small board before also adding a sticker.

Black and white shots of waves crashing against and around a small light house, afterwards fade to black. In the next shots, a person in a wet-suit is using a screwdriver and a knife to attach something to a small board before also adding a sticker. The sticker has a red pattern on a transparent backing and is attached with both hands. The board has a line in the same red all around.

Black and white shots of waves crashing against and around a small light house, afterwards fade to black. In the next shots, a person in a wet-suit is using a screwdriver and a knife to attach something to a small board before also adding a sticker. The sticker has a red pattern on a transparent backing and is attached with both hands. The board has a line in the same red all around. The screwdriver is used to make a hole in the board at 14.5cm.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 9
descriptions: A woman leaves her home and locks the door. She double-checks that the door is actually locked. The next shot shows her from behind walking next to a street to her left. In front of her on the right, a man is sitting on a stone bench.

A woman leaves her home and locks the door. She double-checks that the door is actually locked. The next shot shows her from behind walking next to a street to her left. In front of her on the right, a man is sitting on a stone bench. The woman is wearing a long brown coat over black pants and shirt, the man wears a dark-blue vest over a light-blue sweater. The woman has a small purse with orange and red squares on the front.

A woman leaves her home and locks the door. She double-checks that the door is actually locked. The next shot shows her from behind walking next to a street to her left. In front of her on the right, a man is sitting on a stone bench. The woman is wearing a long brown coat over black pants and shirt, the man wears a dark-blue vest over a light-blue sweater. The woman has a small purse with orange and red squares on the front. The doors to her home is white and there is a glass pane in the wall next to it. Bicycles and cars are parked on the street in front of her home.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 10
descriptions: A man is sitting outside in front of flowers with a wall covered by a large graffito. In the next shot, a different man stands in a tool shed holding a tool similar to an axe.

A man is sitting outside in front of flowers with a wall covered by a large graffito. In the next shot, a different man stands in a tool shed holding a tool similar to an axe. The first man has a mustache and glasses and wears a gray pullover over a green shirt. The second man has a gray beard and wears a jacket over a blue shirt.

A man is sitting outside in front of flowers with a wall covered by a large graffito. In the next shot, a different man stands in a tool shed holding a tool similar to an axe. The first man has a mustache and glasses and wears a gray pullover over a green shirt. The second man has a gray beard and wears a jacket over a blue shirt. Behind him stands a ladder and there are several shovels on the back wall of the shed.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 11
descriptions: A deer is looking directly into the camera. The next shot shows a tractor driving across a field. Afterwards, tall crops are shown from below.

A deer is looking directly into the camera. The next shot shows a tractor driving across a field. Afterwards, tall crops are shown from below. The deer has antlers and white spots on its back. It stands on a green meadow.

A deer is looking directly into the camera. The next shot shows a tractor driving across a field. Afterwards, tall crops are shown from below. The deer has antlers and white spots on its back. It stands on a green meadow. The tractor is red with white markings and pulls a plowing attachment.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 12
descriptions: A diver is shown floating upright under water. The next few shots show a diver swimming under water.

A diver is shown floating upright under water. The next few shots show a diver swimming under water. The diver wears full scuba-gear with a pressurized air tank on their back. The suit is mostly dark with some red accents.

A diver is shown floating upright under water. The next few shots show a diver swimming under water. The diver wears full scuba-gear with a pressurized air tank on their back. The suit is mostly dark with some red accents. In the last shot, the diver is shown swimming in front of a coral rife together with a small fish, examining it.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 13
descriptions: A man sits on a chair and talks to the camera, to his right and slightly behind him is a bicycle. The next shot shows several bicyclists coming around a curve on a street, followed by a car. The next two shots show the group of bicyclists first from the front and then from the side.

A man sits on a chair and talks to the camera, to his right and slightly behind him is a bicycle. The next shot shows several bicyclists coming around a curve on a street, followed by a car. The next two shots show the group of bicyclists first from the front and then from the side.  The man in the chair has dark hair and wears a dark jacket with green zippers. The bicycle next to him has a white frame.

A man sits on a chair and talks to the camera, to his right and slightly behind him is a bicycle. The next shot shows several bicyclists coming around a curve on a street, followed by a car. The next two shots show the group of bicyclists first from the front and then from the side.  The man in the chair has dark hair and wears a dark jacket with green zippers. The bicycle next to him has a white frame. The cyclists in the next shots all wear mostly white helmets, and team jerseys in black, grey, red and white. The man in the first shot, who is the manager of the team, can be heard talking during the entire sequence.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 14
descriptions: A man is standing next to a bed, putting on socks. The next shot pans over some beds, the last one being occupied. Afterwards, a person is shown sitting in a wheelchair and the last shot shows two people sitting at desks in an office.

A man is standing next to a bed, putting on socks. The next shot pans over some beds, the last one being occupied. Afterwards, a person is shown sitting in a wheelchair and the last shot shows two people sitting at desks in an office. The desks have keyboards and CRT-monitors on them. A person in a blue sweater walks in and hands something to the person at the desk further away from the camera.

A man is standing next to a bed, putting on socks. The next shot pans over some beds, the last one being occupied by a person holding a teddy-bear which waves to the camera. Afterwards, a person is shown sitting in a wheelchair in front of an indoor fireplace and the last shot shows two people sitting at desks in an office. The desks have keyboards and CRT-monitors on them. A person in a blue sweater walks in and hands something to the person at the desk further away from the camera. There is narration during the entire sequence

tasks.name: KIS Textual 15
descriptions: A man is shown operating a lathe. In the next shot, he is talking to the camera before a fade to black. The last shot shows a downwards pan over a shelve of cameras.

An older man in a checkered shirt is shown operating a lathe. In the next shot, he is standing in front of a shelve filled with cameras, talking to the camera before a fade to black. The last shot shows a downwards pan over a shelve of cameras.

An older man in a checkered shirt is shown operating a lathe. In the next shot, he is standing in front of a shelve filled with cameras, talking to the camera before a fade to black. The last shot shows a downwards pan over a shelve of cameras. During the whole black and white sequence, he can be heard narrating in Italian.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 16
descriptions: Two people standing in front of a truck loaded with fruit, when a taxi slowly drives backwards and collides with the truck. The driver of the taxi gets out and all three inspect the point of collision.

Two people standing in front of a truck loaded with fruit at night, when a taxi slowly drives backwards and collides with the truck. The driver of the taxi gets out and all three inspect the point of collision. While they are looking, they are blocking the road, and several people ask to be let through.

Two people standing in front of a truck loaded with fruit at night, when a blue taxi with a large horizontal yellow stripe slowly drives backwards and collides with the truck. The driver of the taxi gets out and all three inspect the point of collision. While they are looking, they are blocking the road, and several people ask to be let through. The whole sequence has yellow subtitles, which translate the dialogue to English.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 17
descriptions: A picture-in-picture setup with a small video in the lower left corner of the screen. The large video first shows a bridge, then the sky and finally a view looking up at some outdoor electrical wires and lamp poles.

A picture-in-picture setup with a small video in the lower left corner of the screen with a top-down view of a person walking, wearing green shoes with white accents. The large video first shows a bridge, then the sky and finally a view looking up at some outdoor electrical wires and lamp poles.

A picture-in-picture setup with a small video in the lower left corner of the screen with a top-down view of a person walking, wearing green shoes with white accents. The large video first shows  the underside of a green bridge, then a cloudy sky and finally a view looking up at some outdoor electrical wires and lamp poles.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 18
descriptions: A woman sits up in bed, rests her weight on a chair while getting out of bed and collapses to the floor. The next shot shows her crawling on the floor before a fade to black.

A woman in a hospital gown sits up in bed, unhooks herself from some sort of medical apparatus and rests her weight on a chair while getting out of bed before collapsing to the floor. The next shot shows her crawling on the floor before a fade to black.

A woman in a hospital gown sits up in bed. To her right is a shelve mounted to a wall, to her left is some sort of medical apparatus from which she unhooks herself before resting her weight on a chair while getting out of bed and collapsing to the floor. The next shot shows her crawling on the floor before a fade to black.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 19
descriptions:
The first shot shows a grassy field with two buildings partially visible in the background. Between the two buildings, there is a lot of vegetation. There are a few people walking through the frame from right to left.
The next shot shows two people standing outdoors. Behind and to the left of them, there are several bicycles and behind those a low building. Behind them on the right, cows can be seen.

The first shot shows a grassy field with two buildings partially visible in the background. The building on the left is painted red on the bottom and white higher up while the other building is painted in a light color and has a red roof. Between the two buildings, there is a lot of vegetation. There are a few young people walking through the frame from right to left, all wearing white shirts.
The next shot shows two children in white shirts and black pants standing outdoors. Behind and to the left of them, there are several bicycles and behind those a low building with white walls and green doors. Behind them on the right, cows can be seen.

The first shot shows a grassy field with two buildings partially visible in the background The building on the left is painted red on the bottom and white higher up while the other building is painted in a light color and has a red roof. Between the two buildings, there is a lot of vegetation. There are a few young people walking through the frame from right to left, all wearing white shirts.
The next shot shows two children in white shirts and black pants standing outdoors. Behind and to the left of them, there are several bicycles and behind those a low building with white walls and green doors. Behind them on the right, cows can be seen.
During the sequence, there is narration in French with English subtitles, talking about children going to school.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 20
descriptions: Sequence from an  office setting. A man and a woman are talking about lunch. After the woman gave her food order to the man, another man stands up from behind a room divider and wants some food to be brought to him as well. He gets down and then comes back up again, because he forgot to state his preference for a beverage.

Sequence from an  office setting. A man  with brown hair and a blue sweater over a white shirt and a woman  with short blond hair are talking about lunch. After the woman gave her food order to the man, another man in an orange shirt stands up from behind a room divider and wants some food to be brought to him as well, giving very specific instructions. He gets down and then comes back up again, because he forgot to state his preference for a beverage.

Sequence from an  office setting. A man  with brown hair and a blue sweater over a white shirt and a woman  with short blond hair are talking about lunch. After the woman gave her food order for a burger and a smoothie to the man, another man in an orange shirt stands up from behind a room divider and wants some food to be brought to him as well, giving very specific instructions for three burgers with various extras. He gets down and then comes back up again, because he forgot to say that he also wants a large soda.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 21
descriptions: The camera is moving above a large body of water with the horizon tilted diagonally. The next few shots show a boat with people on it from various angles. In one of the shots, a pirate flag can be seen. The last shot in the sequence pans from the boat with some crew to a small rocky island.

The camera is moving above a large body of water with the horizon tilted diagonally. The next few shots show two people on an outrigger, one person pointing towards an island, a few people next to a pirate flag, the crew of the boat standing in a row and a person tending a flag. The last shot in the sequence pans from the boat with some crew to a small rocky island.

The camera is moving above a large body of water with the horizon tilted diagonally. The next few shots show two people on an outrigger, one person in a blue shirt and red pants pointing towards an island, the name of which is shown on screen, a few people next to a pirate flag, the crew of the boat standing in a row, mostly wearing wet suits and a person tending a flag. The last shot in the sequence pans from the boat with some crew to a small rocky island.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 22
descriptions: The sequence starts and ends with a man standing in a workshop, talking to the camera. In between, he is shown operating a band saw and a drill press.

The sequence starts and ends with a man in a short sleeve dark blue shirt with white text on it, standing in a workshop, talking to the camera. In between, he is shown operating a band saw to cut a piece of metal and a drill press to drill a hole into a metal strip.

The sequence starts and ends with a man in a short sleeve dark blue shirt with white text on it, standing in a workshop, talking to the camera about the process of making parts for cars. In between, he is shown operating a band saw to cut a piece of metal held down with a larger piece of wood and a drill press to drill a hole into a metal strip.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 23
descriptions: A man in blue hat, a black top and jeans is repeatedly attempting to slide down a handrail on a stair way with a skateboard.

A man in blue hat, a black top and jeans is shown getting a running start with his skateboard before he is repeatedly attempting to slide down a handrail on a stair way with a skateboard. Six attempts are shown in total.

A man in blue hat, a black top and jeans is shown getting a running start with his skateboard before he is repeatedly attempting to slide down a handrail on a stair way with a skateboard. Six attempts are shown in total. This is happening during a public event with many people and there is music playing throughout the entire sequence.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 24
descriptions: A man is sitting on a beach next to a canoe, talking to the camera. The next shot shows a baby sea-turtle in the sand.
A man in a white shirt and dark pants is sitting on a beach next to a green and red canoe, talking to the camera. The next shot shows a baby sea-turtle in the sand.

A man in a white shirt with some white text on a green and blue background and dark pants is sitting on a beach next to a green and red canoe, talking to the camera. Some text on the left side on the screen shows his name and occupation. Behind him are some trees and bushes. The next shot shows a baby sea-turtle in the sand.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 25
descriptions: A man is standing center screen behind a sculpture of a large rooster which he is handling. In the next shot, the man sits on a chair next to the sculpture.

A man in a green shirt is standing center screen behind a sculpture of a large rooster which he is handling. In the next shot, the man sits on a chair next to the sculpture with shelves filled with cans of paint and other supplies behind him.

A man in a green shirt is standing center screen behind a sculpture of a large rooster which he is handling. In the next shot, the man sits on a chair next to the sculpture with shelves filled with cans of paint and other supplies behind him. During the whole sequence, the man is talking about mythologies and how animals are used for story telling.

tasks.name: KIS Textual 26
descriptions: A time-lapse view looking up at a building with a statue on top and clouds in the sky before fading to black. The next shots are a slow pan over a bay and a shift in focus from a red flower to a beach behind it.

A time-lapse view looking up at a building with a statue on top and streaking clouds in the sky before fading to black. The next shots are a slow pan over a bay with a large cruise ship in the water and a shift in focus from a red flower in the middle of four vertical branches with green leaves to a beach behind it.

A time-lapse view looking up at a building with a statue on top and streaking clouds in the sky before fading to black. The next shots are a slow pan over a bay with a large cruise ship in the water and a shift in focus from a red flower in the middle of four vertical branches with green leaves to a beach behind it. During the first shot, there is singing in the background, the other shots are accompanied with ukulele music.
